wiki.content: The 212 Songfacts says. The song is named after the area code 212, which covers the area of Harlem, where Banks grew up. It samples the track "Float My Boat" by Lazy Jay, who is credited on the tune. Azealia Amanda Banks is an American rapper, singer and lyricist from New York. Formerly known under the pseydonym Miss Banks, she rose to notability in 2011 whe she topped NME's “Cool List” for the year. Her debut single “212” was released in April 2012.
